  <fr:mainmatter>
    <html:p>The other special kind of function I want to tell you about in this lecture is <html:em>valuations</html:em>.</html:p>
    <html:p>Whenever we talk about valuations, we will always have some collection of things in mind to serve as <html:em>values</html:em>, but what that collection is and what the values represent can vary widely.</html:p>
